This home is conveniently located in a very quiet neighborhood. Very long driveway to your private home with windows to look outside and see birds and enjoy a cup of coffee on your back porch. The ideas here are endless for your joy here in Magnolia Texas.  MOTIVATED NEEDS RESPECTFUL QUICK SELL, THANK YOU.
